  "paths": {
    "/v2/application_mappings/find_by_binary_information": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "CPE mappings for distributable binaries",
        "description": "\n<p>\n  Returns Common Platform Enumeration (CPE) mappings for a given application based on the information that the application's vendor attached to the distributable binary, which can be retrieved via osquery.\n</p>\n\n<div class=\"pin\"><blockquote class=\"callout callout_warn\" theme=\"\ud83d\udea7\"><h3 class=\"callout-heading false\"><span class=\"callout-icon\">\ud83d\udea7</span><p>Restricted Access</p></h3><p>This API endpoint is a premium feature for selected partners.</p></blockquote></div>\n\n<p>\n  To retrieve the vendor/product information from distributable binaries installed on a client machine, run this osquery command:\n</p>\n\n<code>\nosqueryi --json \"SELECT * FROM programs;\"\n</code>\n\n<p>\n  This should produce JSON output which looks like this:\n</p>\n\n<pre><code>[\n  {\n    \"identifying_number\":\"\",\n    \"install_date\":\"20210215\",\n    \"install_location\":\"C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft\\Edge\\Application\",\n    \"install_source\":\"\",\n    \"language\":\"\",\n    \"name\":\"Microsoft Edge\",\n    \"publisher\":\"Microsoft Corporation\",\n    \"uninstall_string\":\"\"C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft\\Edge\\Application\\88.0.705.68\\Installer\\setup.exe\" --uninstall --msedge --system-level --verbose-logging\",\n    \"version\":\"88.0.705.68\"\n  },\n  ...etc\n]\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>\n  The \"publisher\" and \"name\" outputs from osquery map to the \"vendor_name\" and \"product_name\" parameters on this API endpoint. In this case, \"Microsoft Corporation\" and \"Microsoft Edge\":\n</p>\n\n<code>\n/v2/application_mappings/find_by_binary_information?vendor_name=Microsoft Corporation&product_name=Microsoft Edge\n</code>\n\n<p>Results:</p>\n\n<pre><code>{\n  \"cpe_normalized_application_names\": [\n    \"Microsoft Edge\"\n  ],\n  \"cpe_mappings\": [\n    {\n      \"cpe_vendor\": \"microsoft\",\n      \"cpe_product\": \"edge\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"vendor_binary_information\": [\n    {\n      \"vendor\": \"Microsoft Corporation\",\n      \"product\": \"Microsoft Edge\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"vendor\": \"Microsoft\",\n      \"product\": \"EDGE\"\n    }\n    {\n      \"vendor\": \"Microsoft Corp\",\n      \"product\": \"Microsoft Edge\"\n    }\n    ...etc\n  ],\n  \"cpe_application_names\": [\n    \"Microsoft Edge 88.0.705.50\",\n    \"Microsoft Edge 88.0.705.62\",\n    \"Microsoft Edge 88.0.705.63\"\n    ...etc\n  ],\n  \"cpes\": [\n    {\n      \"product_version\": \"-\",\n      \"cpe_uri\": \"cpe:/a:microsoft:edge:-\",\n      \"cpe_uri_format\": \"2.2\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"product_version\": null,\n      \"cpe_uri\": \"cpe:/a:microsoft:edge\",\n      \"cpe_uri_format\": \"2.2\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"product_version\": \"88.0.705.50\",\n      \"cpe_uri\": \"cpe:/a:microsoft:edge:88.0.705.50\",\n      \"cpe_uri_format\": \"2.2\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"product_version\": \"88.0.705.62\",\n      \"cpe_uri\": \"cpe:/a:microsoft:edge:88.0.705.62\",\n      \"cpe_uri_format\": \"2.2\"\n    },\n    ...etc\n  ]\n}</code></pre>\n        ",
        "operationId": "application_mappings-find_by_binary_information",
        "security": [
          {
            "X-Risk-Token": []
          }
        ],
        "tags": [
          "INFERENCE V2 - Application Mappings"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "vendor_name",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "The specified vendor being requested.",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "product_name",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "The specified product being requested.",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "200",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "example": {
                  "cpe_normalized_application_names": [
                    "Microsoft Edge"
                  ],
                  "cpe_mappings": [
                    {
                      "cpe_vendor": "microsoft",
                      "cpe_product": "edge"
                    }
                  ],
                  "vendor_binary_information": [
                    {
                      "vendor": "Microsoft Corporation",
                      "product": "Microsoft Edge"
                    },
                    {
                      "vendor": "Microsoft Edge",
                      "product": "Microsoft Edge"
                    },
                    {
                      "vendor": "Microsoft Corp",
                      "product": "Microsoft Edge"
                    },
                    {
                      "vendor": "Microsoft",
                      "product": "EDGE"
                    }
                  ],
                  "cpe_application_names": [
                    "Microsoft Edge 86.0.622.69",
                    "Microsoft Edge 87.0.664.41",
                    "Microsoft Edge 88.0.705.74"
                  ],
                  "cpes": [
                    {
                      "product_version": "86.0.622.69",
                      "cpe_uri": "cpe:/a:microsoft:edge:86.0.622.69",
                      "cpe_uri_format": "2.2"
                    },
                    {
                      "product_version": "87.0.664.41",
                      "cpe_uri": "cpe:/a:microsoft:edge:87.0.664.41",
                      "cpe_uri_format": "2.2"
                    },
                    {
                      "product_version": "88.0.705.74",
